Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem! Where\Nya goin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you three were unable to\Nretrieve my Bewitching Bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we need another source\Nof great magical power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to defeat Twilight\Nand her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [plodding music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why double-crossing\Nhim with his own bell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,will be so satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If{\i0} we can figure\Nout how to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle\Nmay be the worst....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But she does know stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She once said the\Narchives in Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,has a restricted area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia and Luna love\Nto hoard information
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for themselves. If there's\Nan answer, it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My triumphant\Nreturn to Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the sound of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Road trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt. We\Nknow you're busy planning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Summer Sun Celebration\Nas we requested. But..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Things seem...\Ncalmer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,than we would\Nhave expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No complaints here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With the exception of\Nthe odd trivia night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a lot\Nof progress
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,since the Royal\NSwanifying Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not know this about me,\Nbut I occasionally freak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a joke. I\Nwanted to show you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Summer\NSun Celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,how much I've improved.\NSo I focused on delegating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and trusting others!\NIt's been GREAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's.. actually what we\Ncame to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be the last\NSummer Sun Celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll need to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. It's just\Nthat the Celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,has always been about\Nus. My defeat of Luna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And, thanks to you\Nand your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,my reunion with\Nmy sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're leaving,\Nwe don't see a need
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for the holiday any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister and I have decided\Nthe time for us to retire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is upon us. You and\Nyour friends have proven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you are ready to\Nlead Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So let this be the last\NSummer Sun Celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as Equestria leaves behind\Nthe old to embrace the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness! How are YOU\Nfeeling about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like this could\Ndefinitely send you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,into full\Nfreaky-outy mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually fine. But if\Nthis is going to be the last
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer Sun Celebration,\NI want to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the best\NCelebration {\i1}ever{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't give\Nus more work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't give\Nus more work.....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So even though\Neverything was done,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of a few\Nlast-minute changes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use\Nyour help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord: Oh! The end\Nof a beloved holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Last-minute changes\Nto a celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds positively...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are YOU doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known Celestia and Luna\Nlonger than any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I terrorized them; they\Nturned me into stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is the last\NSummer Sun Situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply can't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I see I've arrived\Njust in time for the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Twilight gives her\Nfriends an impossibly long
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and overly detailed\Nlist" predicament!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess some-draconequis\Nisn't the know-it-all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he thinks he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We were kinda with\NDiscord on this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No more crazy lists.\NNo more freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With your help, I\Nknow we've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Character\Ngrowth is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I at least get\Nmy own note card?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Now, I need to\Ngo rewrite my speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you all look at\Nyour cards, you'll see-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't talk now! Have so much\Nto get done before sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are so many ponies up\Nin the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that silly sun holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How many holidays do you\Nponies HAVE? No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting into the castle\Nwon't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\Nabout that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [sting] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Those are\Nnew. But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [military snare drum] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer. Have to\Nhead inside. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [military snare drum] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [chimes] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [military snare drum] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Of course. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, do yours get glitchy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,More medallions, more\Nproblems. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They've increased\Nsecurity into the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be more\Nchallenging than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you NOT go popping us\Nall over the place please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is of the\Nessence! Let's.. go team!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to know what we're\Ndoing before we go and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, you and I\Nare givin' Braeburn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Appleoosan ponies\Nsome adjustments to the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy and I are meeting\Nthe pegasi from Cloudsdale
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to give them changes\Nto the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, we're going to update\NThe Flaming Sky Firework
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,unicorn troupe with\NTwilight's new vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure Discord doesn't\Ndo anything.. {\i1}Discord-y{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's\Nannoyingly specific...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Increased security on a\Ncrowded holiday with Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and their friends bumbling\Naround? This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. This is perfect!\NWe need a distraction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and those ridiculous\Nponies just gave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, do exactly\Nas I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Step away from the wagons!\NOfficial food tasters here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,on official\Nfood-tasting business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. It ain't gonna be easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think we can whip\Nup these new cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight wants\Nbefore sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If anypony can handle some\Nlast-minute bakin', Braeburn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought plenty\Nfor the celebration,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but if she keeps testin',\Nwe might be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I see a\Nsuspicious-looking COOKIE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [scary music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel... weak\Nall of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is somepony back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony! Get\Naway from the food
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,till we figure out\Nwhat's goin' on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess\Nwants WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what's on that\Nlittle card. No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No big dea..!? It's a much more\Naggressive weather pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then what was\Noriginally ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very irregular!\NWe'll need to-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No! First we must...\NWait! We, Oh..!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it out slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the princess\Nwe will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sure you're\Ndoing an excellent job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yeah. Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna panic\Nand screw it up {\i1}at all{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm not built for\Nhigh pressure situations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly. Sounds like\Nyou need some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony who's organized\Nenough to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the small stuff so you can\Nfocus on the BIG picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The big...? YES!\NThat sounds right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha. This kind of weather\Nhas to be handled delicately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I'm here. I'll\Ntake care of {\i1}everything{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [fanfare] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Flaming Sky Firework\NTroupe is a marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We take pride in what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These last-minute changes\Naren't too challenging,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! The more challenging, the\Nbetter! We aim to {\i1}astound{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you don't mind, we DO\Nhave a new routine to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Horns at the ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Unfortunately,\Nwe have no room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for anypony else at\Nthis time. Ahem. I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Crackle Cossette.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to join\Nyour silly little troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I meant no offense! It\Njust seems a pity for unicorns
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to waste their talents on\Nsomething so... inconsequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicorns wield {\i1}magic{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the most POWERFUL\Nponies in the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever feel you're\Ndestined for more than...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\i1}performances{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all coming together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I really think this is\Ngoing to be the best
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer Sun\NCelebration EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done an\Noutstanding job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've ALL done an\Noutstanding job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be happy to know that\NI have been watching myself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,all night and I have yet\Nto do ONE Discord-y thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna: Now that truly\N{\i1}is{\i0} amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, we know you\Nhad, uh, difficulties
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,using the amulet to\Nraise the sun and moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought perhaps\Na practice session
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,before the festivities\Nmight be in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... a good idea.\NThank you all. So much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am\Nproud'a her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! She\Nfinally realizes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,things will turn\Nout fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,even when she isn't\Nmicromanaging
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,every little detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Braeburn?! What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth ponies. Sick. Food\Nmissin'. Can't.... bake... anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong\Nwith the weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Storms, hurricanes,\Nfog! You name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a disaster\Nout there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Please\Ninform Her Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that we will not\Nbe performing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple fireworks\Nshow is beneath us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're BETTER than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...? Everything\Nwas fine a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, a lot can\Nchange in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's total chaos\Nout there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look\Nat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Do about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What are YOU doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot these.\NYou guys OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, we're\Nsorry but-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But! Er. We don't\Nknow what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,now that everything's\Nall ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was\NTOO organized!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to come up with\Na few last-minute errands
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for you before\Nsunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain to me why we\Ndidn't tell her the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight is finally learning\Nnot to let her stress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,get the better of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If she finds out\Neverything went wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be\Ndevastating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She would be\Nso upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll totally\Nfreak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do\Ny'all suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oo-oo-ooh! Let's just fix it\Nall before she notices!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No lying necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd need a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We HAVE a miracle!\NDon't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I COULD\Nfix everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't the\Nreal miracle here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the miracle of teamwork\Nand character growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord is right.\NTwilight needs US.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happened,\Nwe can fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What DID happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Best. Road trip. EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I was an\Nactual doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have no\Nidea what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta\Nbe a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something got\N'em all sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate the food too! Does\Nthat mean I'm sick? Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [mysterious music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [heroic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\Nthis happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be\NFIRED for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash and\Nthe Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,will have ALL the weather\Nrounded up any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,AHHHH! [thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Archives are in a\Ndifferent part of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What about aiming\Nfor perfection?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've set our\Nsights higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher than perfection?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Higher{\i0} than putting\Non a silly little show
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for the other ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were so excited\Nbefore! What changed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You two just enjoy\Nthe festivities!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a few surprises\Nin store for-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well, don't mind me. I'm\Njust here for the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh-oh. And here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Rainbow Dash doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie? Is\Nthis soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I... was\Nreally hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony understands\Nwanting to take pride
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in your work\Nmore than I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You could do more\Nwith your magic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,than make frilly\Ndresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft! Nopony makes\Nfrills anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This season is actually\Nall about simplicity and-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the point, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I BEG your forgiveness.\NIt's entirely MY fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...um! Just a slight hiccup\Nin the weather! Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack? What\Nis going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I TOLD y'all this\Nwas a bad idea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but nopony ever\NLISTENS TO ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought everything was\Nfine! What is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything {\i1}was{\i0} going fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Until it totally wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to fix\Nit ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't\Nyou tell me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't want\Nyou to freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you thought NOT\Ntelling me everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,was a total disaster\Nwould avoid a freak-out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say it like that, it\Nsounds like a really bad plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how I used to react.\NBut I really have changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Panicking won't\Nsolve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can handle whatever\Nproblems come our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as we handle\Nthem... together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: Spoken like a\Ntrue leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I love a good to-do list!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me exactly\Nwhat happened
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can figure out exactly\Nwhat to do to fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [military snare drum] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:18:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [royal fanfare] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This celebration has\Nalways been a reminder
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,not to fear the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for there is always a new\Nday to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But as we look towards\NEquestria's future,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sad to say that\Ntoday will be the last
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer Sun Celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...because there is something\Neven more important
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two ponies\Nwho have watched over us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,night and day for as\Nlong as we can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We will no longer commemorate\Ntheir battle or their reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, we will take\Nthis day to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,how much they mean\Nto all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day forward\Ntoday will be known as..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Festival of\Nthe Two Sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know\Nwhat to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee hee! A brand-new holiday?\NYou're my kinda princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad we\Npulled it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,About that... We just wanted\Nto say.. we're real sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You did tell us\Nyou'd changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As your friends, we\Nshould have trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you say you're\Nnot gonna freak out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Because I'm sure there's\Ngoing to plenty of things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need my best\Nfriends' help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it really does seem\Nlike you just might be ready
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for whatever comes\Nnext, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So...? Did you find what\Nyou were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I've found success\Nwhere you all find failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have located\Nwhat I sought
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and tomorrow I will set\Nout to retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I return,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria will finally\Nbe ours for the taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop pouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew you couldn't\Nstay that buff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to return all the life\Nforce to those earth ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so Grogar doesn't\Nsuspect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't like\Nthat we worked so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to destroy their party and\Nthey still pulled it off,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't see\NME complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal wasn't to destroy;\Nit was to distract.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we have\Nexactly what we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to master the Bell\Nbefore Grogar returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've managed to stay one step\Nahead of everypony so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.. It really was\Nsuper-easy to get all those
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,earth ponies and\Npegasi and unicorns
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was, wasn't it. Now {\i1}that{\i0}\Nis something to think about...
